assessment_details.task_description:
Brisbane Marriott International has requested a state-of-art review of its operational and management departments so that the hotel’s executive can consider benchmarking.

You are a consultancy team specialising in operational management advice for international hoteliers. You are required to select ONE (1) of the following operational or management departments on which to base your review activities:

Front Office;

Services/Housekeeping;

Food and Beverage;

Finance/Accounting;

Engineering, Maintenance and Security;

Sales and Marketing.

Once you have selected a department, your team (4-5 group members depending on the enrollment) is required to :

search the literature, both academic and trade

use multimedia to present your findings to an assessment panel including Brisbane Marriott International department directors.
